{"id": 2670, "genre": 1000, "title": "今年都有哪些“土味”戳中了你的迷之审美？", "description": "仔细看看，有的“土味”也不是真的土，竟然还有点可爱啊。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 11375, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181210171129femAtpk4POg27sCu.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-11T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5064, "title": "今年都有哪些“土味”戳中了你的迷之审美？", "content": "今年都有哪些“土味”戳中了你的迷之审美？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 315753, "content": "土味美食教程，没打光没取景，但看上去还挺好吃", "image": "img/option/option/20181210230328VzLX1s4mJBKPArSR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315755, "content": "土味表情包，画风简单粗暴，笑点直击灵魂", "image": "img/option/option/20181210230310uCK6BJzNhocSsMPa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315757, "content": "土味情话，可以跟懂的人一问一答抛梗接梗", "image": "img/option/option/20181210230255W4MOAaXy9sKqVCwm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315759, "content": "土味流行歌，朋友唱K炒热气氛必选曲目", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225949JreSLDwW0nokExtA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315760, "content": "土味偶像，挖掘金句和表情包的快乐之源", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225850CO01dXvrU4atRE95.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315761, "content": "土味网红，撇开标签看的话，就是很有梗的普通人", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225749G4JsBkrdSxgbRZtX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315762, "content": "土味时尚，小猪佩琪/全员恶人，是土酷风没错了", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225711m7OdAcIXNC8sUna6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315763, "content": "土味游戏，画风谜之粗糙但就是一直玩不腻", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225651OScUJNAhvaDIWw2t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315764, "content": "我还有别的心头好（请在评论区补充）", "image": "img/option/option/20181210225623qxwtL3ui0peoXCBZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 315842, "content": "都不认识，我精致蓝/吕孩拒绝土味", "image": "img/option/option/201812110956522ng6kH7VtYep9WF4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}